Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂夏海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.19,0:00:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.45,0:00:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼就逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是要罵我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為肯定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定要什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.54,0:00:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳不是又做什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這池塘裡面沒有生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺很寂寥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:38.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以去抓點什麼回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳很喜歡做這種事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒那個心情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給妳零用錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 會給我多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一千円就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我更喜歡諭吉先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:52.44,Default,NTP,405,0,0,,{\fs36}(萬元大鈔)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千円都不會給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五百円
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:00:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我叫大家一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把手錶借給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得在門禁時間之前回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:39.50,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H5FDE72&}{\pos(1135.066,540.866)}大家一起賞月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一屆歡樂釣魚大會要在這個池塘開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位玩得開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實姊也被叫來了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好突然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這是怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:03:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海突然說要去釣魚賺零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說我壞話呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起釣魚更有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.54,0:03:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久沒試過這樣的感覺了 不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木實姊喜歡釣魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.92,0:03:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不算很著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前有時也會和小楓和日影一起去釣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏 在釣什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要釣碉堡的鯛魚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,120,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1005,993)}mede-tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,420,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1203,993)}tai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:27.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是個池塘 鯛魚是釣不到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有鯛魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很想釣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮有時好沒有常識呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不過換成抓貝殼的話 就成了大眼睛的意思了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,540,0,,{\fs48\pos(722,990)}kai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:41.82,Default,NTP,600,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(1287,993)}me-dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H814CF7&\pos(243,156)}me de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H1F82FD&\pos(687,165)}ka i
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.91,Default,NTP,570,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H339A3D&\pos(495,666)}大 眼 睛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳拼成這種意思有什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有魚上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎怎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點拉上來的話就要逃了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.09,0:03:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉回池塘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉地上的話很可憐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這條很大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚到哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那條也不見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了 完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們幾個完全抓不住時機呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏 我撿到一大堆貝殼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏也快點釣起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個池塘沒有大魚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用麵包可能會比假餌更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假餌是人造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚為什麼會來吃人造的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為形狀很像真的食物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有的品種是帶氣味的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魚大概會覺得很美味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和姊姊咬好聞的橡皮擦是同樣的道理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的班導師都一把年紀了還在做這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏沒咬呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咬到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連夏夏也咬橡皮擦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:38.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏釣到什麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是這個池塘的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在坐太空椅嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是大傢伙 釣到大傢伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 去叫人來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有水桶可能會不夠大裝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.83,0:05:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要去另外準備個容器
